---
import PageLayout from "@layouts/PageLayout.astro";
---

<PageLayout>
    <h1 class="p-20 text-center text-white">
        Benicia Middle School<br>
        Parent Teacher Organization
    </h1>

    <div class="flex gap-10 flex-wrap">
        <div class="max-w-96">
            <h2>Volunteer</h2>
            <p>We are still looking for help. We have a couple positions still open on the board. But, we have all sorts of ways you can help.</p>
            <p><a href="https://forms.gle/Dz7rApxM4kJx9M8fA" class="btn">Volunteer Today!</a></p>
            <p>Meetings start at 6 pm at BMS Talk Town on the first Monday of the month, unless there's no school that day.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="max-w-96">
            <h2>Donate</h2>
            <p>A direct do nation to the PTO is a great way for families to help who don't have the time to take on other projects. Contribution, no matter the size, will directly impact our students' education and overall experience at BMS.</p>
            <a href="/donate" class="btn">Donate now</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</PageLayout>

<style>
    h1 {
        background-position: center center;
        background-image: url(/img/yearbook.jpg);
        background-size: cover;
    }
</style>